OL,3,CJob at risk as government takes
OL,4,Ccontrol of UK's third-largest
OL,5,Csteelworks
OL,7,FOne of the UK's biggest steelworks has
OL,8,Fbeen taken over by the government
OL,9,Fafter it collapsed into
OL,10,Fadministration, putting thousands of
OL,11,Fjobs at risk.
OL,13,FSpeciality Steel UK, previously part
OL,14,Fof Sanjeev Gupta's Liberty Steel
OL,15,Fbusiness, employs 1,450 people at
OL,16,Fsites in Stocksbridge and Rotherham.
