OL,3,CJob at risk as government takes
OL,4,Ccontrol of UK's third-largest
OL,5,Csteelworks
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, a specialist insolvency
OL,8,Fcourt heard the company was in
OL,9,Fmillions of pounds worth of debt to
OL,10,Fcreditors but only had #650,000 in its
OL,11,Fbank account.
OL,13,FOn Thursday, the courts granted a
OL,14,Fcompulsory winding up order.
OL,16,FThe company will now be placed in the
OL,17,Fhands of the Official Receiver and
OL,18,Fspecial managers from consultancy firm
OL,19,FTeneo.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
