OL,3,CJob at risk as government takes
OL,4,Ccontrol of UK's third-largest
OL,5,Csteelworks
OL,7,FThe government has agreed to cover the
OL,8,Fongoing wages and costs of the plant
OL,9,Fwhile a buyer is found.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said it remains
OL,12,Fcommitted to the future for steel
OL,13,Fmaking jobs.
OL,15,F"We know this will be a deeply
OL,16,Fworrying time for staff and their
OL,17,Ffamilies, but we remain committed to a
OL,18,Fbright and sustainable future for
OL,19,Fsteelmaking and steel making jobs in
OL,20,Fthe UK."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
