OL,3,CJob at risk as government takes
OL,4,Ccontrol of UK's third-largest
OL,5,Csteelworks
OL,7,FHowever, bosses at Speciality Steel
OL,8,Fsaid the move to wind up the business
OL,9,Fis "irrational".
OL,11,FJeffrey Kabel, chief transformation
OL,12,Fofficer said: "The decision to push
OL,13,FSpeciality Steel UK into compulsory
OL,14,Fliquidation, especially when we have
OL,15,Fsupport from the world's largest asset
OL,16,Fmanager to resume operations and
OL,17,Ffacilitate creditor recovery is
OL,18,Firrational.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
