OL,3,CJob at risk as government takes
OL,4,Ccontrol of UK's third-largest
OL,5,Csteelworks
OL,7,F"The plan that GFG (Sanjeev Gupta's
OL,8,Fparent business) presented to the
OL,9,Fcourtwould have secured new investment
OL,10,Fin the UK steel industry, protecting
OL,11,Fjobs and establishing a sustainable
OL,12,Foperational platform under a new
OL,13,Fgovernance structure with independent
OL,14,Foversight.
OL,16,F"Instead, liquidation will now impose
OL,17,Fprolonged uncertainty and significant
OL,18,Fcosts on UK taxpayers for settlements
OL,19,Fand related expenses, despite the
OL,20,Favailability of a commercial solution."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
