OL,3,CJob at risk as government takes
OL,4,Ccontrol of UK's third-largest
OL,5,Csteelworks
OL,7,FFollowing the news, Charlotte Brumpton-
OL,8,FChilds, GMB National Officer, said it
OL,9,Fis yet "another tragedy" for UK Steel.
OL,11,F"This is another tragedy for UK steel
OL,12,F- and the people of South Yorkshire -
OL,13,Fthis time brought on by years of
OL,14,Fchronic mismanagement by the owners.
OL,15,FBut this represents an opportunity for
OL,16,Fthe Government to take decisive
OL,17,Faction, as it did with British steel,
OL,18,Fto protect this vital UK industry."
